<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="19" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="18.[151,1437,757,2007]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1873,1899]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">Etymology.</emphasis>
I name this species in honor of my good friend and colleague, Dr. Paulo Sergio Fiuza Ferreira (emeritus professor, Federal University of Viçosa, 
<collectingRegion box="[701,852,1909,1935]" country="Brazil" name="Minas Gerais" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">Minas Gerais</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[860,933,1909,1936]" name="Brazil" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">Brazil</collectingCountry>
), who kindly hosted me on several memorable and productive field trips to 
<collectingRegion box="[469,623,1945,1971]" country="Brazil" name="Minas Gerais" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">Minas Gerais</collectingRegion>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
